Set <a data-lt="context-base-iri" href="https://w3c.github.io/json-ld-api/#dfn-context-base-iri" class="internalDFN" data-link-type="dfn" id="ref-for-dfn-context-base-iri-12">base <abbr title="Internationalized Resource Identifier">IRI</abbr></a> in <var>active context</var> to the <a data-link-type="idl" data-xref-type="attribute|dict-member|const" data-link-for="JsonLdOptions" data-xref-for="JsonLdOptions" href="https://w3c.github.io/json-ld-api/#dom-jsonldoptions-base" class="internalDFN" id="ref-for-dom-jsonldoptions-base-4"><code>base</code></a> option from <a data-lt="jsonldprocessor-compact-options" href="https://w3c.github.io/json-ld-api/#dfn-jsonldprocessor-compact-options" class="internalDFN" data-link-type="dfn" id="ref-for-dfn-jsonldprocessor-compact-options-4">options</a>, if set;
            otherwise, if the <a data-link-for="JsonLdOptions" href="https://w3c.github.io/json-ld-api/#dom-jsonldoptions-compacttorelative" class="internalDFN" data-link-type="idl" id="ref-for-dom-jsonldoptions-compacttorelative-2"><code>compactToRelative</code></a> option is <strong>true</strong>,
            to the <abbr title="Internationalized Resource Identifier">IRI</abbr> of the currently being processed document, if available;
            otherwise to <code>null</code>.
